    <p>Stark is portrayed by actor <i>Robert Downey Jr.</i> in the Marvel Cinematic Universe, and has appeared in
        several films including <b>"Iron Man" (2008)</b>, <b>"Iron Man 2" (2010)</b>, <b>"The Avengers" (2012)</b>,
